##########################################################
This is documentation on how to do things on the webpage:

##How to curate tweets for an specific topic (eg. sc)
1.  Go to https://tweetdeck.twitter.com/
2.  Click the + (add column) located on the left bar
3.  Click on collection
4.  Click Create Collection
5.  Find tweets to Add to the collection
6.  Click on the arrows on the bottom-right of the desired tweet, hold, and drag into the Collection column
7.  Click on 'Share'
8.  Click on 'Embed Collection'
9.  Copy that html code line (Modify depending on your preferences. eg size, tweets limit, etc)
